2.3

ACF()

\[ \rho_k = \frac{cov(Z_t, Z_t+k)}{\sqrt{var(Z_k)}\sqrt{var(Z_{t+k})}} \]

Sample correlogram()

X , Y ACF .

  • acf()

  • \(\rho_k = 0\) ACF 0, \(\frac{1}{n}\) ,

  • ACF \(H_0 : \rho_k = 0\)

PACF()

\(Z_t\) \(Z_{t+k}\) \(Z_t, Z_{t+1}, \cdots, Z_k\) \(Z_t\) \(Z_{t+k}\) \(Z_{t+1}, \cdots, Z_{t+k-1}\)

Sample partial correlogram()

X , Y PACF .

  • pacf()

  • ACF
